Class RouteValidationVisitor

java.lang.Object

Ordered, Toggleable, TypeElementVisitor<Object,Object>
@SupportedOptions("micronaut.route.validation") public class RouteValidationVisitor extends Object implements TypeElementVisitor<Object,Object>
Visits methods annotated with HttpMethodMapping and validates the parameters are consistent with the URI.
